descriptionHtml:
Hello!

This is just a very simple mod that I uploaded because I could. The only thing this mod should do is replace the last Breton face preset with this one.

The texture used on the character in the pictures is 'SG Female Textures Renewal' which can be found here:
http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/35267/?
and the body mod is the Sevenbase body which can be found here:
http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/36992/?
Of course you can feel free to use any texture and body mod you like, but this will make the the preset look different.

If this mod does something out of the ordinary (for example, making evil puppies swarm out of your computer (or just glitches out, that too)) don't hesitate to post a comment and tell me how badly I have messed up, so that I am able to work on sorting any problems that you may encounter.

Thanks for looking!
author: Skippy
